{"title":"红花处处开——新民歌选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":3,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花处处开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——新民歌选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工地一朵红花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘今年十八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工地一朵红花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身全是干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热情叫铁熔化！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了厂房早建，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昼夜焊接钢架。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多快好省安全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天大困难不怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焊枪点钢成水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白光蓝焊红霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘轻声一笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抖落万片金花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（甘肃李幼容）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛镐绣江山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历代姑娘弄针线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在炕上绣江山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在姑娘扛镐锨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实地真物绣江山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（天津海河工地）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片石堆得高似山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群姑娘把石搬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霎时再到此处看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人和片石都不见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（天津海河工地）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进工地，举目望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个小伙子真正棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胳膊根子粗又圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮肤黑红亮堂堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头戴草帽小打扮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裤腿挽到膝盖上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锨耍得快又熟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锨准有几十斤强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向前，仔细望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看是谁家的好儿郎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定睛瞧，吃一惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是位大姑娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（天津海河工地）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女下田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自古以来分界线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小妇女不下田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今妇女变了样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑米打柴力量强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕田耙田又种田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心为了千斤粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（浙江奉化）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘栽秧像绣花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘栽秧像绣花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三角丛植要数她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵手巧栽得快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杆红旗跟着她。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贵州周培中）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年干劲冲破天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘栽秧心里甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地组成绿缎子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引动织女下凡间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（云南玉溪杨暄春）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大牛拉着犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女紧扶起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是初学的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天十亩几。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（云南玉溪王家稼）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女要开拖拉机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年还是旧式犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年换上新农具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年实现机械化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女要开拖拉机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贵州潘启风）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两牛拉犁急如风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双铧翻土快如龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说新式农具重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘扶起脸不红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贵州江口）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛过蜜蜂采花忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯曲曲羊叮河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊叮河畔柞林多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片柞林绿似海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹叶儿笑呵呵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养蚕姑娘一群群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鸡未叫入柞林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柞蚕食叶声如雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘越听越欢欣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚕儿吃叶挂树梢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一株树上千万条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹树枝迎风舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像银铃满山摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光开放遍地香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜蜂采花做蜜糖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘往来柞林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛过蜜蜂采花忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贵州株丰）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}